Package com.example.group1hrmsapp.model

Class TimeOffRequest

java.lang.Object
com.example.group1hrmsapp.model.TimeOffRequest
All Implemented Interfaces:
Subject, java.io.Serializable
@Entity
public class TimeOffRequest
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable, Subject
This entity class represents a time off request made by an employee in the HRMS (Human Resource Management System) app. It is also a subject in the observer pattern, which means it can be observed by other objects.
